This album was first reported on 25 June 

2011.
The album, Welch's Gallery, contains 18 scanned images of the complete  
pages of Alan Dart's copyrighted sewn toy patterns. Each scan is of such  
quality that they can be downloaded to obtain the patterns, which
infringes  
Alan's copyright, and is illegal. Below is url of the album and the urls
of  
a representative 5 (of 18) of the images.
